---
import ZhLayout from '../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="DGSDK | 工业自动化与静电消除解决方案"
  description="东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司，专业生产静电消除器、工业清洁机、自动化设备和精密CNC零件。服务全球工业客户。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/"
>
  <!-- 首页横幅 -->
  <header class="masthead hero-slider">
    <div class="hero-slides">
      <div class="hero-slide hero-slide-1 active" style="background-image: url('/assets/img/header-bg.jpg');"></div>
      <div class="hero-slide hero-slide-2" style="background-image: url('/assets/img/portfolio/hero-2.jpg');"></div>
      <div class="hero-slide hero-slide-3" style="background-image: url('/assets/img/portfolio/hero-3.jpg');"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <div class="masthead-subheading">东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司</div>
      <div class="masthead-heading text-uppercase">静电消除器 · 清洁机 · CNC制造</div>
      <p class="hero-desc">为电子、SMT、光学薄膜、自动化设备和精密制造提供专业工业解决方案。</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-xl text-uppercase quote-btn" href="/zh/contact">获取报价</a>
    </div>
    <button class="hero-arrow hero-prev" type="button">‹</button>
    <button class="hero-arrow hero-next" type="button">›</button>
    <div class="hero-dots">
      <button class="hero-dot active" type="button"></button>
      <button class="hero-dot" type="button"></button>
      <button class="hero-dot" type="button"></button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- 核心产品 -->
  <section class="page-section" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">核心产品</h2>
        <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">先进的工业解决方案，提高效率、减少缺陷、优化生产流程。</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator" class="product-card">
            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-bolt fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
            </span>
            <h4>静电消除系统</h4>
            <p>高性能离子设备，消除静电，提高生产稳定性，适用于电子、SMT及包装生产线。</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <a href="/zh/products/automation" class="product-card">
            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-gears fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
            </span>
            <h4>自动化系统</h4>
            <p>定制自动化解决方案，简化工作流程，提高生产效率，降低人工操作成本。</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts" class="product-card">
            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-industry fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
            </span>
            <h4>精密CNC零件</h4>
            <p>严格质量控制的高精度CNC加工，稳定公差，性能可靠，支持OEM定制。</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="product-card">
            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
              <i class="fas fa-soap fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
            </span>
            <h4>工业清洁机</h4>
            <p>适用于PCB、FPC、SMT、偏光片、背光板和光学薄膜制造的精密清洁设备。</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/zh/products" class="btn btn-warning text-uppercase px-4 py-2">查看所有产品</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 应用领域 -->
  <section class="page-section bg-light" id="portfolio">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">应用领域</h2>
        <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">了解我们的解决方案如何提高效率、减少缺陷、优化生产线。</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
          <a href="/zh/applications" class="portfolio-item app-card">
            <div class="portfolio-link">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/img/portfolio/1.jpg" alt="电子制造" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-caption">
              <div class="portfolio-caption-heading">电子制造</div>
              <div class="portfolio-caption-subheading text-muted">静电控制与清洁解决方案</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
          <a href="/zh/applications" class="portfolio-item app-card">
            <div class="portfolio-link">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/img/portfolio/2.jpg" alt="SMT生产" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-caption">
              <div class="portfolio-caption-heading">SMT生产</div>
              <div class="portfolio-caption-subheading text-muted">工业自动化与设备支持</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4">
          <a href="/zh/applications" class="portfolio-item app-card">
            <div class="portfolio-link">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/img/portfolio/3.jpg" alt="精密加工" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-caption">
              <div class="portfolio-caption-heading">精密加工</div>
              <div class="portfolio-caption-subheading text-muted">高精度CNC零件解决方案</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-warning text-uppercase px-4 py-2">讨论您的应用需求</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 关于我们 -->
  <section class="page-section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">关于史帝克</h2>
        <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司</h3>
      </div>
      <ul class="timeline">
        <li>
          <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/1.jpg" alt="公司成立" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="timeline-panel">
            <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>2013年成立</h4><h4 class="subheading">专业工业制造商</h4></div>
            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">史帝克成立于东莞，专注于工业自动化、静电消除系统和精密制造解决方案，服务全球客户。</p></div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="timeline-inverted">
          <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/2.jpg" alt="技术发展" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="timeline-panel">
            <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>技术扩展</h4><h4 class="subheading">静电控制与清洁解决方案</h4></div>
            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">我们扩展了产品范围，包括适用于电子、SMT和光学薄膜行业的静电消除器和工业清洁机。</p></div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/3.jpg" alt="先进制造" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="timeline-panel">
            <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>制造能力提升</h4><h4 class="subheading">自动化、静电控制、CNC</h4></div>
            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">我们的核心业务现涵盖自动化系统、静电控制设备、清洁机、精密CNC零件和OEM制造服务。</p></div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="timeline-inverted">
          <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/4.jpg" alt="全球服务" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="timeline-panel">
            <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>全球服务</h4><h4 class="subheading">长期工业合作</h4></div>
            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">史帝克以稳定的产品质量、工程支持和实用的工业解决方案为全球客户提供长期合作服务。</p></div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 资质认证 -->
  <section class="page-section bg-light" id="certifications">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">资质认证</h2>
        <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">认证质量与国际合规</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-grid">
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert1.png" alt="证书1" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert2.png" alt="证书2" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert3.png" alt="证书3" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert4.png" alt="证书4" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert5.png" alt="证书5" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert6.png" alt="证书6" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert7.png" alt="证书7" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert8.png" alt="证书8" loading="lazy" /></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 获取报价 -->
  <section class="quote-section" id="contact">
    <div class="quote-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container quote-content">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="quote-title">获取免费报价</h2>
        <p class="quote-desc">如果您需要了解我们的产品，请填写以下表格提交询价，工作日24小时内回复。</p>
      </div>
      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mkopvoyk" method="POST" class="quote-form">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="您的姓名（必填）" required />
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="您的电子邮箱（必填）" required />
        <input type="text" name="phone" placeholder="您的电话号码" />
        <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="请输入您的询价内容" required></textarea>
        <!-- honeypot -->
        <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
        <button type="submit">发送询价</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhLayout>
